                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='15804' id='15' type-v2='text' w='99064' x='468' y='16336'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='11'>Key Insights</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>• Tennis and Football led the dataset in average performance.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>• Recovery did not fully align with performance, suggesting multiple factors influence output.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>• Athletes with 8+ hours of sleep recorded the highest average performance.</run>
                      <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='11'>• High performers also showed higher fatigue and lower recovery, suggesting a tradeoff between output and readiness.</run>
